   Community Affairs Program

                              MISSION STATEMENT

   To promote compliance with the fair lending laws and regulations,
   including the Community Reinvestment Act (CRA), the Equal Credit
   Opportunity Act (ECOA), the Home Mortgage Disclosure Act (HMDA), and
   the Fair Housing Act (FHA).

   The CAP assists consumer and community groups, government officials,
   financial institutions, examiners and other interested groups and
   individuals in understanding and participating in the CRA, including
   community development, and fair lending process.  The CAP also supports
   the FDIC's compliance examination function as it relates to CRA,
   community development and fair lending.

